{
  "stem": "20710.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hmm, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was still 19-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] No, I'm talking already-- I got in, already, to the 1942.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, this was already in fall 1942.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they started making ghettos, you know, to concentrate from all these small towns, and villages, and this, and even-- and the big cities, to put all these, you know, Jewish people in one area, that they wouldn't, you know-- a ghetto, that I'm sure you--",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans, and they tried to clean out all the other places, to, to, to make unify, to take away all the Jews, and then to put them in the one area, and to have them there.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we, we knew this, this started in different-- first, it started in Lwow, in the big city.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they started in the smaller.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took us to-- the, the nearest city was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they made, there, a ghetto, one part of the city.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they fenced it around with wire, with this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they, they, you know, tried all these Jewish people that there were in surrounding towns, to put them in there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this all-- yeah, this happened in sometimes in December.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And how did you know you had to go to the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because we knew-- because they started, like in Lwow, they started in other cities.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we knew that that's what-- I mean, I guess they were clear that that's what they going to do.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They, they going to, to come-- I mean to take the Jewish people in one area, in certain areas, and have them all together.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't go because that time my mother [INAUDIBLE] my parents were very concerned.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, you know, we are older.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
